title: Savant Garde
description:
Ladies and gentlemen, this torrent contains Image Comics' Savant Garde. 


This series was a spin-off from the WildC.A.T.S. series and it featured the character, Savant and a team of heroes that she gathered. Members included Majestic, Cybernary, Disperse, Sheba and Met-L.

The book ran 7 issues in 1997and featured the creative team of Story: Barbara Kesel, Pencils: Ryan Odagawa, Inks: Chuck Gibson

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources who shall remain nameless.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
